The following test always shows the original message "This is my fail!" in the stack trace to me. Even for depth 1000. 

```java
    public void testRecursiveException() {
        doTestRecursive(1000);
    }

    private void doTestRecursive(int x) {
        if (x <= 0)
            throw new IllegalStateException("This is my fail!");

        try {
            doTestRecursive(x - 1);
        }
        catch (Exception e) {
            throw new IllegalStateException("Not my fail!", e);
        }
    }
```
